             was indicted for <rs id="t18291029-238-off1344" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18291029-238-off1344" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18291029-238-off1344" type="offenceSubcategory" value="simpleLarceny"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18291029-238-cd1345" type="crimeDate">16th of October</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18291029-238-off1344 t18291029-238-cd1345"></join>, two phosphorus-boxes, value 3d.; 1 newspaper, value 2d.; 2 snuff-boxes, value 1s.; 2 jars, value 4d., and 1 book, value 6d.
            </rs>, the goods of 
               
                  <persName id="t18291029-238-victim1930" type="victimName">
                     Henry Francis 
                     Piaget
                  <interp inst="t18291029-238-victim1930" type="surname" value="Piaget"></interp>
